a <i>Δh2</i>, etc.,

174
00:13:21,754 --> 00:13:26,361
to finish at <i>Δhn</i> and terminate
at the point <i>B</i>,

175
00:13:26,361 --> 00:13:30,485
and the sum of these differences 
of level or vertical drops

176
00:13:30,485 --> 00:13:34,691
give the height between 
point <i>A</i> and point <i>B</i>.

177
